reviewText:
Don't let the cutesy cover fool you, fitness dash is game with unparalleled depth in the RPG / Sim / fitness genre. The bulk of the challenge comes from watching your fat American customers shed pounds on the treadmill, while cleaning up their dirty towels and getting them more water. This takes a lot of skill and is no easy feat, believe me.

I cannot praise this game enough, it will forever be a classic in gaming history.

Also please, give me your password.
